Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.19,0:21:33.77,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.77,0:21:35.20,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,排擠人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.47,0:21:37.86,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,好 今天也要工作 工作
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.33,0:21:41.00,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,還要給這幢公寓招租
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.28,0:21:42.48,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,要忙起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.78,0:21:47.28,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,琴音 加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.64,0:21:48.17,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,好
